quote: "The sea sings below the waves,"
subject: Modern Nature Poetry in South America
permalink: /Modern Nature Poetry in South America/Cecilia Vicuña/Cecilia Vicuña - Songs of the Sea
---

The sea sings below the waves,
a deep and vibrant blue,
tales of journeys lost and found,
a map of dreams across the horizon.

And we, like sailors, navigate,
touched by the mystery of tides,
drawn to what lies beyond,
a promise of adventures uncharted.

- Cecilia Vicuña
